ussr to cut coal price for japan steelmil the soviet union ha agr to cut it coke coal export price to japan steel mill by about five dlr a tonn in 1987/88 start april 1 in exchang for an increa in export volum , industri sourc said . the price were set at 44 dlr a tonn for neryungrinski coal and at 43.80 dlr for kuznetski coal , fob . japan will import a total of 4.9 mln tonn from both area , up from 4.2 mln a year earlier , they said . the steelmak had ask moscow to agr to a cutback to 3.7 mln tonn in 1987/88 , but the soviet union urg japan to increa the amount to 6.5 mln , they said .